content.detailedDescription:
approx. last september my wife and i, who live in santa monica, were spending the day in downtown los angeles.

it was approx. 4 pm. there were no clouds in the sky. 

we were seated in a park approx 100 yards north of los angeles city hall, enjoying the day.

glancing upward, i noticed, almost directly overhead but slightly eastward, an object hovering and changing colors.

the object appeared to be very high in the sky. 

for example, in downtown los angeles, one can see commercial airplanes heading toward burbank or at their cruising altitude.

this object appeared, to me, to be much higher.

i pointed the object out to my wife. 

we watched the object hover in place for approx. 10 minutes. the entire time is systematically changed colors from white to green to red to blue.

what really struck me was that the sky was blue, not a cloud to be seen, yet this blue color being given off by this object was clearly seen as blue against the blue sky. 

after approx. 10 minutes the lights slowly moved westward until we lost sight of the object.

again, this object was so high in the sky that several times i lost track of it and my wife, with sharper vision than i, had to point it out to me again.

after losing sight of it, we walked to chinatown and, upon our return toward city hall, looking up, the object was again hovering overhead, having returned.

after a while it slowly moved away and, again, being so high up, it was difficult to track, we lost sight of it. 

in my opinion, the only reason we could see it at all was due to the changing colors.

with respect,

~taylor brandon
content.summary: High altitude object over los angeles changing colors

content.detailedDescription: I went outside to smoke a cigarette around 10:30 last night. it was brighter out than normal for that time of night, so i was looking up at the moon trying to see if there was a full moon. to the right of the moon i noticed a star that looked bigger and way brighter than every other star in the sky. then i saw the red light moving and initially rubbed my eyes thinking i was just seeing things. but the lights kept changing. i kept seeing the red light go by rotating from right to left. so i focused on several other stars thinking it's just got to be my eyes, but no other star in the sky did anything like that. so i started to take pictures, it was hovering so high up in the sky. i watched it for around a half an hour while it changed lights the entire time,as im mstill trying to figure out what it was. when i came back outside around a half hour later it was gone. i was excited when i first saw it, but the longer i watched it change and hover above i got nervous. i'm still not positive what exactly happened last night. so it would be nice to know,if anyone else in the area saw the same thing.
content.summary: I watched it hover for about a half an hour it changed lights white and red going from right to left

content.detailedDescription: I was outside approx 9:30p.M. checking my sprinklers. looked up to need and bright orange-red pulsating object was flying directly towards me at approx 90748158300-1000' alt. observed object with some sort of coronal ejection of bright colored lights out of bottom of orb. my first thought was it appeared to be in distress. the orb was ejecting lightning like light from bottom of orb. and it appeared to be slowing. at approx 1000' from my position i could see the orb flashing internal lights of yellow and white that appeared to be almost like fire. i could hear no sounds from orb. then orb went from pulsation to flickering orange-red light until orb went black. there is a full moon tonight which backlit the shape of the craft. when it was descending we could see clearly the outline and that it had been changing direction and hovering. approx size estimates 200-300' craft shaped possible round or square. approx distance of landing site up to 1 mile away. we witnessed the craft descend between the house across the street and their tree. when it reached the top of the tree behind them we lost sight. approx 1second afterwards we witnessed impact flash. we went looking for craft since i know approx location of impact due to hunting in area. however, we were unable to locate any evidence of landing or possible crash due to night and vast rural areas and adjacent to foothills.
content.summary: 3 witnessed object fly, flame and sparks came out of bottom then stopped. pulsation went dark, object descended then we saw impact flash. went looking could not find at night or in approx area.

content.detailedDescription: I was finishing up playing with my brother outside in our front yard when i saw it up in the sky. i looked at it as it rushed by because it looked like a computer glitch (or when a line of pixels on your tv stops responding).  it was way above the clouds and was about the size of a small pill from my point of view. it looked like it was a bright led light outline of what looked to be a rectangle with its center invisible, or two halves of a square that were slightly separated.  it came from nowhere in the sky, and then was suddenly rushing away within the span of a second before it had blipped out of existence again. while i was able to see it it either left behind a short broken up neon trail or part of the square's own line had extended back behind it somewhat. i was completely stunned because whatever i had seen had gone by so fast and was so high above the clouds that i couldn't believe that it was anything like a plane or helicopter and instantly believed that it was something i was not supposed to necessarily see. i was completely silent and stopped moving in awe when i watched it zip by and instantly told my brother what i had seen right afterward. i told him of the distance at which it had been from me, the size, the speed, and specifically the odd square neon shape.  he believed that it could not have been a plane or anything and said that it was either a ufo or some sort of military secret aircraft.  this was all unbelievable, but also odd, because this was the first time i had been back home in a month, and certainly the first time i had played outside with my brother in a long time.  i don't know if any of this matters but my brother and i were playing badminton, then practicing balancing and swinging either an 11 foot stick of bamboo or a baseball bat.  i had also been telling my brother earlier about a remote control plane a friend of mine had made recently, if any of that mattes at all. also, after i told my brother i went inside and told my parents, who then went outside to look for themselves after i had drawn them a small picture of what it had looked like. they believed me, but didn't see anything. it reminded my mother of times in the past where she had believed she'd seen ufos. i took a snapchat of the sky where i saw it and drew in the shape i had seen (although i drew it a little large) but didn't post the snap, but just kept it to remember what i'd seen.
content.summary: Looked like an outline of neon led lights that almost made a square. very fast and far away.

content.detailedDescription: I had just driven two hours from ct. i had jut pulled into my driveway in the berkshires, and got out of my car and looked up. i had noticed a lot of fireflies on my drive so maybe i was looking up to see if we had any near my own home. i then noticed these very subtly colored lights kind of clustered together but moving apart. there were four and most of them were bluish and one orangey and they were all moving very steadily like how satellites move. now i have been camping many times and have seen satellites cross the sky. i was surprised that there were four. and i kept staring to try and decide if they really were colored and it wasn't just becausei had been driving. but they were definitely colored and i noticed that two were smaller and more blue. the other two were larger and one was blue-green and the other red-orange. they were not particularly bright: about as bright as the other stars in the sky. the two blues were changing angle from more of a 60 degree down to 55, 50, 45, etc. moving ne towards southern vermont. they were kind of paired but not extremely close to each other. the larger blue-green light was moving downs similar angles but heading nw towards southern vermont over clarksburg state forest. the larger red-orange one was maintaining a the 60 angle and was moving w/sw. they felt like they were moving at the speed that a satellite moves across the sky (slightly faster than your average commercial airplane). i watch for approximately  30  seconds, questioning everything: if these are satellites, why can i see colors? and why are they different colors? and four at the same time? and all crossing paths from a similar point in the sky? after those thirty seconds and looking into my phone to see if i could take a picture, the orange one changed path now heading nw towards the blue-green light over clarksburg state forest and towards southern vermont. i immediately called my best friend. she did not answer. phone rang about 4/5 times until voicemail greeting and automated instructions. i then left about a 45 second voicemail narrating what i had seen and what i was seeing. during this time, an airplane entered the my vision heading nw in the same direction as the orange-red and the blue-green lights over clarksburg state forrest and towards southern vermont. this had your standard blink red and white lights that are typically seen on commercial flights. the two smaller blue ones left my field of vision (there are a lot of houses and mountains) and then slowly the larger blue-green and red-oranges faded into the distance with the airplane still heading in the same direction. it was warm out about 65 degrees f and it had been up in the 80s that day. there had not been any precipitation that day nor for the couple of days prior. there were not many if not none clouds. (not edited for spelling, capitalization or grammar).
content.summary: 4 satellite-like different colored lights moving away from the same point. two went one direction, one went one direction, one went another direction but then changed path to other join other lone one.

content.detailedDescription:
Several of my family members launched approximately 15 balloons secured together at a park.  balloons went towards the sun and we watched them for quite some time. several pictures were taken of the event.  upon viewing the pictures, a purplish figure type object was seen above the balloons and the sun to the left of the photo.  a green orb was below the balloons to the right.  these were all in a direct line. the green orb, then balloons (going towards the sun) then the purplish object.  the purplish object/figure looked like a face book friend request icon. i don't know any other way to describe it. 

the sun was very bright so we did not notice anything until we saw the pictures.  

our family is torn on what this was.  it was very strange that it was all in a line.  since this was a memorial for a family member, i'd like to think the purplish object was my family member waiting to receive the balloons, and my husband thinks the green orb may have been some type of ufo.  

we have never seen this type of thing in a picture, so thought it might be worth investigating.

the pictures were forwarded on face book, so although no one actually physically witnessed the light and object, several people did notice it in the pictures.
content.summary: Picture was taken of a balloon launch. green orb appeared in picture in 5 different images, different spot in each picture

content.detailedDescription: My husband was out side around 9 :00pm saturday night 6/18/16 and called for me  to come to the front yard. when i came out i saw several round/ oval reddish orange yellow brightly colored objects flying lower than an airplane but no obvious wings or sound. as we watched there were  12 to 13 unidentifiable objects  flying nw over fields in west iredell county statesville nc . we have never seen anything like this before. we tried to imagine  what would look like these objects. we did consider hot air balloons but we live in area that has a lot of hot air balloons and these were not.  they were not flying fast but were following one another in a nw direction.  finally there were no more as they flew out of sight.  all this took about 15 minutes. my husband went into the house but i stayed a while longer to see if there were any more. when there was not i went back into the house too. i believe in extraterrestrial beings but this was the first time i have witnessed any thing that could be considered a ufo. there could be a plausible explanation and i hope there is.  i did try to find out if anyone else reported seeing these colorful bright things but could not find such a report. today i was telling friends about this experience and they just chuckled. that is when i decided to submit this report. they may think it is silly but i do not.
content.summary: 12-13 ufos were seen from our front yard around 9:00pm. it took about 10-15 minutes for all craft to fly by

planes rare at midnight esp sat/sun midnight. tiny airport 3 mile nw

content.detailedDescription: Last night at 8:45 pm, i saw a spherical object with lights that appeared to be spiraling cross my field of vision.  when i first noticed, it was directly in front of me moving north east.  i watched for 5-7 seconds and it had no wings, sound or trail.  i estimate it was at 10,000 - 20,000 feet of altitude and travelling 500 mph or more.  i ran for my camera and began taking a video about 15-20 seconds after i first saw it.  by this time, it was to the extreme north east.  the camera was fully zoomed in and i tried to crop out parts of the video where nothing was visible and also zoomed in on my computer.  this was not a plane, nor satellite.  the sky was till very bright and i cannot explain what i saw.  i have attached both the cropped and original video.
content.summary: At 8:45 pm before sunset i saw a spherical object with lights and i took a video

content.detailedDescription:
9:45 pm, 6/18, watching tv in living room.  to the right of my tv is my vaulted ceiling dorm window. a super bright solid orange oval passes right through the window frame.  very interruptive!  at first thought, i sat up and leaned just a bit wanting an explanation.  a second exact same thing goes through the window.  i jumped up and ran to the front door located under the same dormer window.  sure enough they were and more coming from the west over the houses tops.  i ran back inside and woke my wife.  pulled her out to see.  she saw the 2 coming at us from the west still in our direction. they were all in line and beginning to turn away towards the right as they neared.  asked my wife to get her cell.  more were still coming from the west toward us and then veering away towards the right.  i grabbed her phone and held the camera up way high.  pressed the button  while reaching straight up at them.  by this time it was the last two still in view before the trees and over my neighbors house. the shot is attached.    

i did within the next 20 minutes or so go back outside just in case i figured, and my neighbor was coming round the corner in his car.  he also saw the objects as well as his daughter who was still home just down the street.

also i noted there was no wind.  dead silent outside.  the lighting was dusk and moon was near full.  very clear overall.

i called eugene pd 541-682-5111 and 911 and asked both if anyone else reported anything.  they said no.
content.summary: Multiple extremely bright orange, solid, no sound, no wind, in line up. got picture w trees, clouds & house in photo  . photo shakey.

content.detailedDescription:
I walked outside to put my dog on the line. the line is attached to the soffit below the roof, so you have to look up in the air, to hook her up.

there was a town celebration 2 blocks away. i could hear the band singing, but not clear enough to make out the words. it was a beautiful clear night. 
 
there was a perfect view of the moon. there were only 2 stars in the sky. the north star and one that was much lower in the skyline. 

i immediately saw a bright yellow fireball object traveling in a straight line, in my direction. it was high above the trees, but much lower than airplanes travel from cincinnati to louisville, and in the wrong direction.

i starred and thought to myself, what is that? planes fly above my house north to southwest, and vise versa. it came from the east and moved straight over my house and continued heading west. there were no red or blue lights, nothing flashing, like planes have. it did not make any sound and was traveling much faster across the sky, than a plane does. 

the fireball was solid yellow, and appeared to be the size of car. as it got closer it appeared to have an orange ring around it. only when it was directly above my head, did i see, the fireball was in the center and there was a red laser grid (in a rectangle shape)surrounding the entire fireball. this was only visible when it was directly over my head (like looking up through the bottom of a lamp shade).  the red laser lines did not connect to the fireball, but they had several lines connecting to each other all around the fireball. it never stopped or slowed down. 

there was no sound, my dog didn't look up, she immediately ran down the line (sniffing for rabbits) on her way to the pine trees, 150 ft. away. she never barked. my eyes were locked, i never looked away. 

i yelled "come here" and started pointing to the west as it was passing over my house. my adult son, was standing 6 feet away, in the sunroom, (looking at the tv). he walked outside while i was yelling "look at that do you see it?" i had grabbed his bicep, in the process. he said "yes i see it, what was it?""your scaring me mom". i said, "sorry, i just wanted to make sure you saw it too". i went straight in the house, looked at the kitchen clock (it was 10:35 pm) and ran to the bathroom to tell my fianc'.
content.summary: Yellow fireball traveling in a straight line red laser grid around it

content.detailedDescription:
At a farm in the united kingdom i was approached by a young looking blonde haired blue eyed 5ft 9 inch tall 170lbs man with a stun gun type technology.
the man put the stun gun to my heart area of my chest and pressed the trigger. at first it did not work probably due to by thick coat as it was cold that night. the second or third shot finally worked and i was shot dead by the stun gun type technology that looked alien in it's appearance. 

my body fell forward to the floor on the grass field but my i found my self still stood up and i could see my body lieing on the floor. i was now in the same dimension as the aliens and i could now see that their was a sphere silver exterior style flying saucer parked on the field about 100 feet away which had windows and inside i could see it had different rooms and the interior was red padded seats. this appeared to be the one dimension higher than the 3rd . perhaps the 4th. i could see cars driving past and everyone i could still hear and see the sound and light from the 3rd dimension but nobody could see me. except anyone in this now higher dimension. i quickly noticed that i was in soul form in the 4th or higher dimension. i tried to fight with the extraterrestrial as he walked quickly back to the ufo 100 feet away asking him to put my soul back in my body that was laying on the field at night with the nearest people about another 100 feet away as i was staying at a farm house that night. 

the human/nordic looking extra terrestrial refused to put me back in my body and instead got insdie his beam ship. 

another nordic/human extraterrestrial appeared in the craft , female , long dark , wavey hair, about 5ft 1 and 150lbs. she was seen at the window. and speaking telepathically to me through the window.

i remember her clearly saying the words '' yoo , hoo , kevin '' as if i was an animal and not a human.

30 seconds later another ship arrived about 100 feet from the ufo with the two nordic type being inside. this other ship was larger , rectangular and extra dimensional as the inside looked larger than the outside. 

the second space craft came down from space very quickly and it has what looked like nano crystals as it's fuel source. the craft contained draconian, reptilian brown scaled and black scaled beings.

around 8 of the black draconian/reptilian type beings exited the ship and stood on the ground trying to scare me. instead not knowing what else to do , i actually ran towards the 8 black scaled draconian beings and fought fieacfully for around 2 minuetes. in this dimension i felt much lighter and i was able to life 2 of the draconians as high as the nearest electrical power line and slammed both of them into it and it made a dent in the power line in that dimension but not in the 3rd where i noticed a car driving past the road at the point in the 3rd dimension. a man was driving the car and he seemed to noticed something from the 3rd dimension because when the draconians hit the electrical power line the man quickly turned his head at the power line in the car as if he noticed something but couldent see exactly what it was.


after the fight. nearly all draconian soldiers were injured and two seriously injured with one of them i am not sure if he died as he was taken inboard the ship by another extraterrestrial that was not nordic looking or reptilian looking. where he was first treated with a medicine crystal that wa sbeing orbited by another crystal in its stationary position. that being was then moved into another room. the ship seemed to be much larger inside than outside and there was lots of beings walking about further down the ships internal corridor. 

for a moment there was a what appeared to be a (pretend) ship laser gun fight between the flying saurcer and the draconian ship. 

then the draconians must of asked for some help as a large grey appeared to the right of the 2nd ship another 30 feet to the right of the 2nd craft.
